title: forum software SUCKS
body: Please fix this.  Cannot post on anything, it keeps saying I'm under level 7 when I'm not.

replies.body: Hey, it sounds like your profile needed to sync to the boards.  There is a[ profiling syncing tool](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool) pinned at the top to help with this too, but you should be okay now!
